Detailed Description

cvmx_sso_xaq::_head_ptr

These registers contain the pointer to the first entry of the external linked list(s) for a particular group. Software must initialize the external linked list(s) by programming SSO_XAQ()_HEAD_PTR, SSO_XAQ()_HEAD_NEXT, SSO_XAQ()_TAIL_PTR and SSO_XAQ()_TAIL_NEXT to identical values.
